OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F: Thousands descend on     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FCardiff in subsidy plan row
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F- BBC News                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, At the moment the main scheme for      
OL,6, subsidising farmers across Britain is  
OL,7, the basic payment scheme (BPS).        
OL,9,FIt provides an annual payment to most  
OL,10,Ffarms - the rate of which depends on   
OL,11,Flocation and land type.                
OL,13,FBut after the UK left the European     
OL,14,FUnion, a new scheme to support         
OL,15,Fagriculture had to be drawn up.        
OL,17,FThe BPS will continue until 2025 across
OL,18,Fall nations - but England and Wales    
OL,19,Fplan on phasing it out from then.      
